de.take_weiland.mods.commons.config

Annotation Type GetProperty


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=FIELD)
public @interface GetProperty
    Annotate a field with this to inject a configuration property into it.
    The field has to be static and of type int, boolean, double or String (or an array of those).

    Use ConfigInjector.inject to populate all fields having this annotation
    The field's initial value will be used as the default
    Author:
    diesieben07
    See Also:
    Configuration

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      java.lang.String category
      the category for this property
      defaults to Configuration.CATEGORY_GENERAL unless @Item or @Block are present as well
      java.lang.String comment
      a comment for this property
      defaults to no comment
      java.lang.String name
      the name of the property to inject into this field
      defaults to the field name
